---
title: Mexican Beef Mince & Black Bean Chilli with Garlic Rice, Cucumber Salsa & ‘Mayo’
description: Say hello to the best bean in town, nutrient-packed black beans. They are wholesome and filling and go perfectly in a bowl with garlic rice and a fresh cucumber salsa. Now cook up beef mince and add it to the chilli to really drive home those mouth-watering flavours.

